data.description: Enjoy the country atmosphere while still being close to town with this 3 bedroom, 2 bath Colonial home on 1 acre! Most rooms have hardwood floors and are spacious – even the laundry room and bedrooms! A couple rooms need some TLC, but so much other work has already been done:  water heater replaced in 2021, breaker box recently replaced, air vents cleaned in 2023, attic access stairway installed, metal roof on house and garage. The 22'x40' garage can easily accommodate 3 cars. There are 2 storage sheds in the backyard. This home has so much potential and predictable expenses for improvements. Sold as-is. Full general inspection can be provided by realtor, by request. Schedule your showing today!
